title: Daily Review with Clay and Buck - Dec 2 2021
itunes:title: Daily Review with Clay and Buck - Dec 2 2021
description:
Senator Ted Cruz on vaccine mandates and why the Women's Tennis Association has bigger balls than the NBA. MS Governor Tate Reeves on one of the most consequential pro-life legal battles of our time.  Jen Psaki says the pandemic is to blame for crime. Happy Birthday to our longtime EIB engineer Mike!
